  "title": "Corporate Secretarial Admin (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties:</strong><br />- Manage a range of mail-related tasks, including coordination, redirection, collection, sorting, and document scanning</p><p>- Support the processing and digitalisation of statements, letters, and other important documents</p><p>- Assist with administrative duties such as scanning records, preparing required documents, and updating internal systems</p><p>- Help maintain accurate data entry, handle routine updates, and support document-tracking processes</p><p>- Update and manage profiles in internal platforms, conduct basic screenings, and perform follow-ups for required information</p><p>- Monitor alerts, track outstanding reviews, and ensure timely completion of assigned compliance or verification tasks</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />- Diploma graduate in any field<br />- Minimum 1 year of relevant work experience<br /></p><p>Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now</p><p>Chow Zi Qing<br />R2199258<br />Revup Proservices Pte Ltd<br />EA.24C2366</p>",
